		h4 Animated content
		p If you wish to have some nice &amp; simple animated content showed when a slide is active, 
			| please add some special classes to the elements as showed in the below screenshot. 
			| Remember to specify the 
			strong position:absolute 
			| as well as 
			strong top, left 
			| position of each "appear-*" element.
